## 🚀 Installation

### **Option 1: Install from Source**

```bash
# Clone repository
git clone https://github.com/Abdur-azure/lmtool.git
cd lmtool

# Install in development mode
pip install -e .

# Verify installation
lmtool --help
```

### **Option 2: Install via pip** (when published)

```bash
pip install lmtool
```

### **Verify Installation**

```bash
lmtool version
```

**Output:**
