## ⚡ Quick Start

### **1. List Available Options**

```bash
# List training methods
lmtool list-methods

# List evaluation metrics
lmtool list-metrics
```

### **2. Train a Model**

```bash
# Quick training with defaults
lmtool train quick gpt2 ./data.jsonl ./outputs

# Or with full options
lmtool train run \
    --model gpt2 \
    --dataset ./data.jsonl \
    --method lora \
    --epochs 3 \
    --output ./outputs
```

### **3. Evaluate the Model**

```bash
# Quick evaluation
lmtool evaluate quick ./outputs ./test.jsonl

# Or with specific metrics
lmtool evaluate run \
    --model ./outputs \
    --dataset ./test.jsonl \
    --metric rouge1 \
    --metric bleu
```

