### **`lmtool train quick`**

Quick training with sensible defaults.

**Usage:**
```bash
lmtool train quick <model> <dataset> <output>
```

**Example:**
```bash
lmtool train quick gpt2 ./data.jsonl ./outputs
```

Equivalent to:
```bash
lmtool train run \
    --model gpt2 \
