### **`lmtool train resume`**

Resume training from checkpoint.

**Usage:**
```bash
lmtool train resume <checkpoint_dir> --epochs <additional_epochs>
```

**Example:**
```bash
lmtool train resume ./outputs/checkpoint-100 --epochs 2
```

