Reason: Most memory efficient, enables large models on consumer hardware

Memory Estimates:
  full_finetuning: 112.0 GB
  lora: 56.0 GB
  qlora: 14.0 GB
  available: 12.0 GB

Alternative Methods:
  • None (insufficient memory for other methods)
```

