## 🆘 Troubleshooting

### **Command Not Found**

```bash
# Verify installation
pip show lmtool

# Reinstall
pip install -e . --force-reinstall
```

### **CUDA Out of Memory**

```bash
# Reduce batch size
lmtool train run ... --batch-size 2

# Enable gradient checkpointing
lmtool train run ... --grad-checkpoint

# Use QLoRA
lmtool train run ... --method qlora --4bit
```

### **Slow Training**

```bash
# Increase batch size (if memory allows)
lmtool train run ... --batch-size 8

# Reduce max length
lmtool train run ... --max-length 256

# Limit samples for testing
lmtool train run ... --max-samples 1000
```

